Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.91,0:00:21.77,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}俺が捨てた道具は ギルベルトの犬になった
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.93,0:00:26.15,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}だが両腕を失い あるじを失い
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.89,0:00:29.10,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}なにもかもなくしたその果てに
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.32,0:00:33.88,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}なぜかそこに立っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.44,0:01:29.51,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ありがとうございます
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.03,0:01:42.04,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}甘いな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.51,0:01:44.77,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}時間切れだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.51,0:01:49.57,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}さっさと私を殺していれば間に合ったかもしれんものを
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.72,0:01:51.75,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}爆弾か
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.26,0:02:02.72,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}緊急停止！ 急げ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.55,0:02:08.12,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}利かない？ 客車のブレーキを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.52,0:02:09.40,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}非常ブレーキ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.16,0:02:23.75,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}何だ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.42,0:02:39.24,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヴァイオレット
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.84,0:02:51.63,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヴァイオレット
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.55,0:02:53.77,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}もう1つの爆弾を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.31,0:02:55.03,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}分かった
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.35,0:03:04.15,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}外れた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.37,0:03:12.13,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヴァイオレット
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.28,0:04:20.18,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヴァイオレット
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:33.65,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ガルダリクおよびライデンシャフトリヒの両国は
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.03,0:04:36.29,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}国際平和と安全を維持するために
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.75,0:04:40.96,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}主権を有する対等の関係として相互に連携を行う
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.44,0:04:46.10,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そのために ただちに公正な貿易を再開し
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.68,0:04:53.12,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ライデンシャフトリヒは友好の証しとして 緊急支援物資を1年分提供する
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.86,0:04:59.39,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以上ここに両国の和平を調印することを誓う
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.71,0:05:07.51,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}終わりました
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.63,0:05:12.28,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}どうした
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.14,0:05:16.05,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}終わったのに…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.63,0:05:19.69,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}終わったのに…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.55,0:05:22.48,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}戦争は終わったのに
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.18,0:05:25.08,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}息子は帰ってこない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.92,0:05:30.29,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}もう息子は諦めようと妻に言ってるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.03,0:05:32.84,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}でも…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.27,0:05:35.14,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}分かります
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.05,0:05:39.64,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}よく 分かります
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.16,0:05:46.72,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}手紙にはこう書いてくれるかな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.14,0:05:53.02,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}俺たちの所に生まれてきてくれてありがとうって
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.29,0:05:56.80,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}はい
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.43,0:06:03.16,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}では航空祭事務局のほうへ このお手紙を届けておきます
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.74,0:06:07.33,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}当日このお手紙が空から届けられますので
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.97,0:06:13.08,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}自動手記人形サービスのご利用 誠にありがとうございました
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.62,0:06:16.20,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}遅くまでご苦労様
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.08,0:06:19.25,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お客さん多くて大変だったでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.91,0:06:20.87,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}問題ありません
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.21,0:06:26.67,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}航空祭 しばらく戦争で中止になってたし
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.31,0:06:30.68,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}5年ぶりだから みんな楽しみにしてるのよね
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.70,0:06:35.73,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明日が諦め切りだから もう1日頑張りましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.43,0:06:39.14,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}はい 頑張ります
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.29,0:06:46.73,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私もね 手紙書こうかなって思ってるの
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.77,0:06:50.58,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ドールになる前 私踊り子してたの
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.51,0:06:53.70,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お店には軍の人もたくさん来てた
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.44,0:06:57.64,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}亡くなった人もずいぶんいてね
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.73,0:07:02.11,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}その人たちに書こうかなって
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.96,0:07:06.51,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヴァイオレットも書いてみたら
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.92,0:07:13.39,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私はまだ自分の手紙を書いたことがありません
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.76,0:07:18.08,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}じゃあ記念すべき初めての手紙ね
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.81,0:07:23.65,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今のあなたが思うとおりに書けばいいのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.66,0:07:26.20,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}心のままにね
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.36,0:07:29.26,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}心の…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.65,0:07:35.24,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.50,0:07:37.06,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}何だ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.04,0:07:39.76,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私はもうご不要ですか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.93,0:07:42.14,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}何のことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.77,0:07:44.26,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}処分される結果
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.76,0:07:47.47,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ホッジンズ中佐のもとへ移されるのでしょうか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.09,0:07:52.64,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}もう少佐に命令は頂けないのでしょうか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.98,0:07:58.33,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}君はそんなに私の命令が欲しいのか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.06,0:08:00.71,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}命令は私のすべてです
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.15,0:08:06.83,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私の命令は この戦い以降聞かなくていい
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.95,0:08:10.92,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いや 誰の命令も聞かなくていい
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.84,0:08:12.82,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}自由に生きなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.96,0:08:16.81,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}それがご命令ですか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.72,0:08:21.91,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}どうして命令だと思うんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.36,0:08:27.38,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私が 本当に道具だと思っていると
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.03,0:08:33.00,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そっなのであれば幼い君を抱いて帰りはなしなっかた
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.47,0:08:37.19,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}君をずっと私だけのそばに置かなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.87,0:08:38.85,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}分かっているはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.99,0:08:42.77,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怒っているのも つらいのも君を…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.90,0:08:47.23,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少佐…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.03,0:08:49.63,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}君には感情がある
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.68,0:08:52.74,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私と同じ心があるだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.88,0:08:55.07,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ないというのなら
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.56,0:08:57.94,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ないというのなら その顔は何だ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.46,0:09:00.33,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そんな顔ができるんじゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.97,0:09:05.07,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今私のことが怖いだろう 急にどなられてイヤだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.00,0:09:06.83,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}分かりません
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.66,0:09:10.03,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}理不尽に言われて 腹が立つだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.10,0:09:10.95,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}分からません
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.31,0:09:12.27,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ウソだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.11,0:09:15.38,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ウソではありません…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.13,0:09:19.74,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}自分でも分からないのです
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.18,0:09:25.55,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私は 少佐の命令を聞いていたいのです
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.80,0:09:30.43,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少佐の命令があれば どこにでも行けるのです
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.04,0:09:33.38,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}それだけなのです
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.53,0:09:41.60,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}すまなっかた
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.59,0:09:48.60,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}でも私は君が自分は道具であれと戒めるのを見ているのが
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.73,0:09:50.57,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}つらい
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.27,0:09:52.52,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小さかった君を
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.91,0:09:57.57,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そんなふうにしてしまったのは 私なのに
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.76,0:09:59.70,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}なのに
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.05,0:10:03.52,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}君はまだ私のことを信じて
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.36,0:10:15.48,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}君は悪くない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.08,0:10:20.89,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}もう数時間で決戦だ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.66,0:10:24.16,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}この話は また今度にしよう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.79,0:10:31.83,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}書けなかった?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.27,0:10:36.32,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}心はあるのです
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.07,0:10:39.54,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あったのです あの時も
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.29,0:10:42.97,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ですが 分からないのです
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.09,0:10:46.98,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少佐に何を伝えたいか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.59,0:10:48.50,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヴァイオレットちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.09,0:10:52.75,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}まだ時間はあるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.86,0:10:55.68,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}締め切りは今日の夕方だけど
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.13,0:10:59.05,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}朝までに書ければ 俺が事務局に持っていく
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.17,0:11:01.19,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}だから書くんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.34,0:11:05.52,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}短くても 1行でもいいから
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.14,0:11:10.90,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}はい
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.89,0:11:12.89,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}失礼します
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.92,0:11:19.30,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あの ヴァイオレットにブーゲンビリアさんとおっしゃるお客様が
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.87,0:11:23.29,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ありがとうございました
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.80,0:11:30.64,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}こっちだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.33,0:11:44.00,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}昨日まで航空祭の手紙の代筆で忙しかったんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.56,0:11:48.91,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今日は休みなのに 会うのが俺で悪っかた
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.49,0:11:50.23,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いえ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.71,0:11:54.25,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ライデンのうちの屋敷には来たことはなっかたな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.14,0:11:56.95,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}驚かないように言っておくが
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.96,0:12:00.13,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少し記憶が曖昧になっている
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.82,0:12:10.55,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}母だ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.78,0:12:15.74,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あなたは
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.11,0:12:19.13,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヴァイオレットです
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.77,0:12:22.33,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}母上が会いたいと
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.48,0:12:28.35,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そうだったわ あの子がここに引き取ってほしいと
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.86,0:12:31.44,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}やっと来たのね
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.00,0:12:33.80,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}はい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.75,0:12:35.54,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あら
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.42,0:12:40.04,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}でも もっと小さな女の子だと思っていたのだけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.07,0:12:42.16,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あれは いつ？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.31,0:12:44.28,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}4年前です
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.79,0:12:46.29,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ああ そうね
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.86,0:12:49.29,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}フォルネムの本宅から連絡が
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.24,0:12:52.08,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ギルベルトは一緒ではないの
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.08,0:12:55.43,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}母上 ギルベルトは…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.78,0:13:00.54,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一緒です
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.46,0:13:10.01,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あの子の瞳と同じ色だわ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.51,0:13:16.08,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少佐の瞳と同じ色です
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.93,0:13:21.45,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}美しいわね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.06,0:13:24.00,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}はい
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.66,0:13:28.34,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}言葉が分からなかったので 言ったことはありませんが
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.15,0:13:30.23,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少佐の瞳は
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.85,0:13:33.43,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}出会った時から美しいです
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.19,0:13:37.48,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}美しいです
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.14,0:13:43.94,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}それで あなたギルベルトとはどういう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.63,0:13:52.05,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少佐は私を拾い 育て 使ってくださいました
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.06,0:13:53.83,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ですが…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.73,0:14:02.32,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}分かってるわ インテンスの戦いであの子は
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.95,0:14:08.00,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そうです その話をするために来てもらったのでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.51,0:14:09.24,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}母上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.10,0:14:12.32,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そうだったわね
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.85,0:14:23.75,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あなたのせいではないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.23,0:14:28.15,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あなたが背負わなくていいのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.24,0:14:35.28,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ディートフリートはね もうギルベルトのことは諦めろと言うの
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.26,0:14:39.82,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あの子だって できはしないのに
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.30,0:14:46.60,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}2人はね 子供の頃からそれは仲のいい兄弟だったのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.23,0:14:52.96,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あの子は生きてる
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.31,0:14:57.80,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}心の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.01,0:15:02.88,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}だから決して忘れない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.58,0:15:08.65,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}思い出すたびにつらくても ずっと想って生きていくわ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.34,0:15:11.41,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}だって今も
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.51,0:15:16.98,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}愛しているんだもの
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.64,0:15:21.44,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}はい
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.19,0:15:26.06,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}はい
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.20,0:15:31.00,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}はい
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.95,0:15:46.87,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヴァイオレット
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.26,0:15:52.01,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あいつの分も お前は生きろ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.85,0:15:55.40,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}生きて 生きて 生きて
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.50,0:15:59.69,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そして死ね
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.59,0:16:04.96,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}これが俺からの最後の命令だ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.53,0:16:08.50,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}もう
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.84,0:16:12.42,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}命令はいりません
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.49,0:16:31.00,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}俺が捨てた道具を
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.64,0:16:34.40,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ギルベルトは道具として扱わなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.44,0:16:41.15,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}だから それは両腕を失い あるじを失っても
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.80,0:16:44.79,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あいつからもらった大切なものを
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.88,0:16:49.83,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}決して なくすことはないだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.80,0:17:35.82,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}本当いい天気になってよかった
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.29,0:17:39.27,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ライデンには珍しく雪が降りましたもんね
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.05,0:17:41.96,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ローランド
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.48,0:17:44.45,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あれ 手つないでる
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.06,0:17:46.46,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}すごいですね
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.81,0:17:47.80,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いいなあ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.27,0:17:50.20,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヴァイオレット
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.40,0:17:53.15,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ルクリア
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.73,0:17:55.70,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}よかった 来られたのね
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.35,0:17:59.59,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}航空祭の代筆であなたも忙しかったでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.18,0:18:01.78,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いえ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.64,0:18:05.57,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}でも たくさん手紙を書きました
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.61,0:18:09.68,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}初めて 自分の手紙も
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.03,0:18:16.98,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そっか 私も書いたわ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.45,0:18:18.43,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}両親宛てに
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.09,0:18:23.11,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}きっと届きます
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.69,0:18:25.51,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.05,0:18:27.26,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私も書きましたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.13,0:18:29.53,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}未来の自分に
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.83,0:18:31.41,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ライデン一 いや
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.69,0:18:34.30,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大陸一のドールになってる自分に
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.58,0:18:36.05,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}すごい野望ね
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.36,0:18:39.59,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}エリカさんは 何を書いたんですか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.73,0:18:46.73,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最近好きな人ができたので その人に気持ち…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.02,0:18:50.33,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誰ですかそれ 誰ですか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.87,0:18:55.37,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}俺の手紙の内容知りたいか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.71,0:18:56.70,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}知りたい
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.05,0:18:58.01,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ああ…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.39,0:19:01.07,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}実はさ ホッジンズ宛に書いたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.44,0:19:06.10,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}将来 俺が社長になるって
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.38,0:19:08.49,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お前 俺にとって代わる気か
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.60,0:19:10.02,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}何てこと書いてんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.69,0:19:12.29,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人のこと言えないでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.82,0:19:14.77,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あなただって 何書いてんのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.17,0:19:18.10,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}パパから未来の娘へ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.16,0:19:19.26,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いつの間に…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.45,0:19:20.61,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}やめて
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.55,0:19:27.15,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}書き損じた手紙が 社長室のゴミ箱からいっぱいあふれ出てたわよ パパ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.34,0:19:29.26,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}君がパパと呼ぶな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.34,0:19:30.91,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}パ パ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.63,0:19:33.72,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}やめろ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.07,0:19:37.78,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}パパは君が生まれるのを待ってるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.00,0:19:45.16,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そして祈ってる 君がすくすく育つことを
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.36,0:19:48.01,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}幸せになることを
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.15,0:19:52.05,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誰かを愛し 愛されることを
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.67,0:19:57.74,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そして君や君の子供たちの生きる未来が
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.91,0:20:04.47,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}争いのない 幸せであるれた世界でありますようにと
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.96,0:20:46.07,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}たくさんの人の想いが 空から降ってきます
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.15,0:20:50.08,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヴァイオレット
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.17,0:20:59.01,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.93,0:21:04.49,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}親愛なるギルベルト少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.75,0:21:12.41,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お元気ですか お変わりないですか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.42,0:21:15.85,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今どこにいらっしゃいますか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.17,0:21:19.38,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}困ったことはありませんか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.19,0:21:28.72,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}春も夏も秋も冬も
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.80,0:21:31.73,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いくつも季節が過ぎましたが
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.50,0:21:36.54,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少佐のいらっしゃる季節だけが 巡ってきません
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.49,0:21:41.53,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私 最初は分かりませんでした
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.83,0:21:46.50,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少佐のお気持ちが 何一つ分かりませんでした
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.80,0:21:52.86,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}でも 少佐に頂いたこの新しい人生の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.44,0:21:58.40,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少しだけですが 感じることができるようになったのです
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.52,0:22:01.76,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}代筆を通して
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.07,0:22:04.90,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}出会った方たちを通して
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.39,0:22:12.37,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私は信じています
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.51,0:22:17.73,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少佐が どこかで生きていらっしゃることを
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.37,0:22:20.66,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}だから私も 生きて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.79,0:22:24.95,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}生きて 生きて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.12,0:22:29.35,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}その先に何があるか分からなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.01,0:22:31.11,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ただ生きて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.39,0:22:36.81,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そして また会えたら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.53,0:22:39.00,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}こう伝えたいのです
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.57,0:22:42.57,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私は 今
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.38,0:22:44.51,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}愛してるも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.23,0:22:55.76,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少しは分かるのです
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.01,0:24:18.51,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヴァイオレット 代筆依頼 至急の用件だって
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.59,0:24:21.60,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ベネディクト お前お茶いれてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.06,0:24:24.46,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}何だよ 何で俺がお茶を
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.11,0:24:32.04,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヴァイオレットちゃん お客様がお待ちだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.78,0:24:39.46,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今 行きます
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.48,0:26:29.02,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お初にお目にかかります
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.95,0:26:33.29,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お客様がお望みなら どこでも駆け付けます
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.22,0:26:35.95,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}自動手記人形サービス
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.94,0:26:42.99,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヴァイオレット·エヴァーガーデンです
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,ch
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.91,0:00:21.77,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}{\blur7.5}我抛弃的道具成为了基尔伯特的狗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.93,0:00:26.15,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}{\blur7.5}可是失去了双臂 失去了主人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.89,0:00:29.10,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}{\blur7.5}在失去了一切后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.32,0:00:33.88,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}{\blur7.5}不知为何 她仍然站立着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.44,0:01:29.51,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}{\blur7.5}非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.03,0:01:42.04,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}{\blur7.5}天真
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.51,0:01:44.77,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}{\blur7.5}时间快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.51,0:01:49.57,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}{\blur7.5}要是早点杀掉我的话也许还来得及
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.72,0:01:51.75,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}{\blur7.5}有炸弹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.26,0:02:02.72,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}{\blur7.5}紧急停车！赶快
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.55,0:02:08.12,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}{\blur7.5}没用？用客车的刹车
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.52,0:02:09.40,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}{\blur7.5}应急刹车
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.16,0:02:23.75,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}{\blur7.5}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.42,0:02:39.24,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}{\blur7.5}薇尔莉特
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.84,0:02:51.63,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}{\blur7.5}薇尔莉特
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.55,0:02:53.77,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}{\blur7.5}还有一颗炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.31,0:02:55.03,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}{\blur7.5}明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.35,0:03:04.15,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}{\blur7.5}拆掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.37,0:03:12.13,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}{\blur7.5}薇尔莉特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.28,0:04:20.18,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}{\blur7.5}薇尔莉特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:33.65,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}{\blur7.5}加达里克与莱顿沙夫特里希两国
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.03,0:04:36.29,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}{\blur7.5}为了维护国际和平与安全
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.75,0:04:40.96,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}{\blur7.5}以拥有主权的对等关系相互合作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.44,0:04:46.10,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}为此 立即重启公正的贸易
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.68,0:04:53.12,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}作为友好的证明 莱顿沙夫特里希将提供一年份的紧急支援物资
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.86,0:04:59.39,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}至此 两国宣誓签署和平协议
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.71,0:05:07.51,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.63,0:05:12.28,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.14,0:05:16.05,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}明明结束了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.63,0:05:19.69,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}明明结束了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.55,0:05:22.48,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}战争明明已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.18,0:05:25.08,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}儿子还是没回来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.92,0:05:30.29,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}妻子都劝我放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.03,0:05:32.84,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.27,0:05:35.14,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我理解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.05,0:05:39.64,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我非常理解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.16,0:05:46.72,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}可以帮我这样写吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.14,0:05:53.02,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}感谢你生在我们家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.29,0:05:56.80,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.43,0:06:03.16,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那么这封信将会送到航空节事务局处
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.74,0:06:07.33,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这封信会在当天从天空送达
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.97,0:06:13.08,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}十分感谢您使用自动手记人偶服务
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.62,0:06:16.20,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}辛苦了 工作到这么晚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.08,0:06:19.25,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}客人这么多 想必很累吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.91,0:06:20.87,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.21,0:06:26.67,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}航空节 因为战争中止了很久
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.31,0:06:30.68,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}时隔五年 大家都非常期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.70,0:06:35.73,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}明天就是截止日了 再努力一天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.43,0:06:39.14,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好 我会努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.29,0:06:46.73,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我也想过要不要写封信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.77,0:06:50.58,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}在当人偶之前 我是名舞娘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.51,0:06:53.70,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}店里很多客人都是军人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.44,0:06:57.64,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}死去的人也不少
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.73,0:07:02.11,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我想写信给他们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.96,0:07:06.51,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}薇尔莉特也写写看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.92,0:07:13.39,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我还没有替自己写过信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.76,0:07:18.08,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那就是值得纪念的第一封信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.81,0:07:23.65,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}就按你现在想的写吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.66,0:07:26.20,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}照心里想的写
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.36,0:07:29.26,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}心里…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.65,0:07:35.24,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.50,0:07:37.06,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.04,0:07:39.76,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}您已经不需要我了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.93,0:07:42.14,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.77,0:07:44.26,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}作为处分的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.76,0:07:47.47,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我会被转到霍金斯中佐手下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.09,0:07:52.64,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我再也收不到少佐的命令了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.98,0:07:58.33,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你就这么想要我的命令吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.06,0:08:00.71,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}命令就是我的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.15,0:08:06.83,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这场战斗之后 不用再听我的命令了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.95,0:08:10.92,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不 不用听任何人的命令了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.84,0:08:12.82,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}要自由地活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.96,0:08:16.81,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这就是 您的命令吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.72,0:08:21.91,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你为什么会觉得这是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.36,0:08:27.38,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你真以为我把你当作道具吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.03,0:08:33.00,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}如果是那样的话 我就不会把年幼的你带回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.47,0:08:37.19,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我一直只把你留在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.87,0:08:38.85,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你应该明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.99,0:08:42.77,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}生气也好 难过也好都是把你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.90,0:08:47.23,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}少佐…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.03,0:08:49.63,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你也是有感情的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.68,0:08:52.74,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}和我一样也是有心的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.88,0:08:55.07,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}如果没有的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.56,0:08:57.94,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}如果没有的话 该怎么解释你现在的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.46,0:09:00.33,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你不是会做出这种表情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.97,0:09:05.07,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你现在很怕我吧 不想突然被大声训斥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.00,0:09:06.83,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.66,0:09:10.03,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}被不讲理地教训 很生气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.10,0:09:10.95,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.31,0:09:12.27,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你撒谎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.11,0:09:15.38,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我没撒谎…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.13,0:09:19.74,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我自己也不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.18,0:09:25.55,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我想听到少佐的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.80,0:09:30.43,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}只要有少佐的命令 我去哪里都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.04,0:09:33.38,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.53,0:09:41.60,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.59,0:09:48.60,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}只是我 一直看你将自己束缚成一个道具
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.73,0:09:50.57,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}太难过了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.27,0:09:52.52,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这么娇小的你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.91,0:09:57.57,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}之所以会变成这样 都是因为我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.76,0:09:59.70,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}可是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.05,0:10:03.52,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你还这么相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.36,0:10:15.48,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不是你的错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.08,0:10:20.89,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}几个小时后就是决战了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.66,0:10:24.16,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这些话下次再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.79,0:10:31.83,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}没写出来？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.27,0:10:36.32,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我是有心的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.07,0:10:39.54,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我当时也有心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.29,0:10:42.97,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但是 我还是不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.09,0:10:46.98,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你想对少佐说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.59,0:10:48.50,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}薇尔莉特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.09,0:10:52.75,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}还有时间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.86,0:10:55.68,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}虽然截止时间是今天傍晚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.13,0:10:59.05,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}如果你明早写得出来 我帮你送去事务所
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.17,0:11:01.19,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}所以写吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.34,0:11:05.52,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}再短也行 一行也行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.14,0:11:10.90,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.89,0:11:12.89,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.92,0:11:19.30,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那个 有位叫布干维尔的客人找薇尔莉特
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.87,0:11:23.29,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}多谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.80,0:11:30.64,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.33,0:11:44.00,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}昨天你还在忙着代写航空节的信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.56,0:11:48.91,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}抱歉 明明你今天休息 还让你来见我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.49,0:11:50.23,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}没事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.71,0:11:54.25,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我们在莱顿的宅子 你没来过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.14,0:11:56.95,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}为了不让你太惊讶 先说在前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.96,0:12:00.13,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}她的记忆已经有些模糊了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.82,0:12:10.55,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这是我母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.78,0:12:15.74,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.11,0:12:19.13,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是薇尔莉特
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.77,0:12:22.33,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}母亲说过想见她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.48,0:12:28.35,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}对了 那孩子说希望这里能收留她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.86,0:12:31.44,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你终于来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.00,0:12:33.80,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.75,0:12:35.54,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.42,0:12:40.04,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我还以为是年纪更小一点的女孩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.07,0:12:42.16,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那是在什么时候？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.31,0:12:44.28,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}四年前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.79,0:12:46.29,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}啊 好像是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.86,0:12:49.29,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}福尔涅姆的本家来了联络
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.24,0:12:52.08,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}基尔伯特没在一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.08,0:12:55.43,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}母亲 基尔伯特…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.78,0:13:00.54,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}他在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.46,0:13:10.01,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}和那孩子的眼睛是一样的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.51,0:13:16.08,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}和少佐的眼睛是一样的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.93,0:13:21.45,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}真美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.06,0:13:24.00,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.66,0:13:28.34,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我不懂它的意思 所以没有这么说过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.15,0:13:30.23,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但是少佐的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.85,0:13:33.43,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}从我遇见少佐的时候就觉得它很美
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.19,0:13:37.48,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是很美
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.14,0:13:43.94,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那么 你和基尔伯特之间是怎样的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.63,0:13:52.05,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}少佐他捡到了我 培养了我 驱使了我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.06,0:13:53.83,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.73,0:14:02.32,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我知道 那孩子在因坦斯决战中…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.95,0:14:08.00,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是的 就是为了说这个才让她来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.51,0:14:09.24,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.10,0:14:12.32,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.85,0:14:23.75,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这不是你的错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.23,0:14:28.15,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不用觉得有负担
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.24,0:14:35.28,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}迪特福利特已经劝我别等基尔伯特了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.26,0:14:39.82,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}明明他自己也做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.30,0:14:46.60,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}他们两人从小就是非常要好的兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.23,0:14:52.96,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}他还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.31,0:14:57.80,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}活在心里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.01,0:15:02.88,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}所以绝对不会忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.58,0:15:08.65,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}哪怕每次想起他都会难过 也要一直铭记着他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.34,0:15:11.41,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}因为我现在也
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.51,0:15:16.98,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}依然爱着他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.64,0:15:21.44,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.19,0:15:26.06,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.20,0:15:31.00,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.95,0:15:46.87,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}薇尔莉特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.26,0:15:52.01,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你要连着他的那份 一起活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.85,0:15:55.40,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}一直 一直活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.50,0:15:59.69,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}然后死去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.59,0:16:04.96,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这就是我最后的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.53,0:16:08.50,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我已经
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.84,0:16:12.42,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不需要命令了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.49,0:16:31.00,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我所抛弃的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.64,0:16:34.40,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}基尔伯特并没有把她当成道具
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.44,0:16:41.15,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}所以即使她失去双臂 失去主人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.80,0:16:44.79,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}从他那里得到的宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.88,0:16:49.83,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}也绝对不会遗失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.80,0:17:35.82,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}幸好天气变好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.29,0:17:39.27,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}难得莱顿竟然下雪了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.05,0:17:41.96,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}罗兰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.48,0:17:44.45,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}咦 牵着手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.06,0:17:46.46,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}真厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.81,0:17:47.80,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.27,0:17:50.20,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}薇尔莉特
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.40,0:17:53.15,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}露库莉娅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.73,0:17:55.70,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你来了呢 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.35,0:17:59.59,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你也在忙着写航空节的代笔信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.18,0:18:01.78,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}没有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.64,0:18:05.57,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但是我写了很多封信
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.61,0:18:09.68,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}也第一次替我自己写了信
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.03,0:18:16.98,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这样啊 我也写了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.45,0:18:18.43,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}写给父母的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.09,0:18:23.11,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}一定能传达到的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.69,0:18:25.51,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.05,0:18:27.26,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我也写了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.13,0:18:29.53,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}写给未来的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.83,0:18:31.41,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}莱顿第一 不
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.69,0:18:34.30,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是成为了大陆第一人偶的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.58,0:18:36.05,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}野心真大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.36,0:18:39.59,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}埃丽卡小姐写了什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.73,0:18:46.73,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}最近有了喜欢的人 就把自己的心意…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.02,0:18:50.33,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是谁呀那人 是谁呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.87,0:18:55.37,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}想知道我的信写了什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.71,0:18:56.70,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.05,0:18:58.01,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.39,0:19:01.07,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}其实 我写给了霍金斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.44,0:19:06.10,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}告诉他 将来我会成为社长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.38,0:19:08.49,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你这家伙 想取代我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.60,0:19:10.02,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}怎么写这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.69,0:19:12.29,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}轮不到你说别人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.82,0:19:14.77,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你才是 写什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.17,0:19:18.10,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}爸爸写给未来的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.16,0:19:19.26,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}什么时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.45,0:19:20.61,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.55,0:19:27.15,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}写坏的信纸多到从社长室的垃圾箱里满出来了 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.34,0:19:29.26,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你别叫我爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.34,0:19:30.91,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.63,0:19:33.72,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}住口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.07,0:19:37.78,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}爸爸等待着你的诞生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.00,0:19:45.16,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}并且祈祷你能茁壮成长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.36,0:19:48.01,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你能获得幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.15,0:19:52.05,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你能爱上他人 亦为他人所爱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.67,0:19:57.74,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}也希望你和你的孩子们所生活的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.91,0:20:04.47,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是一个没有纷争 满溢着幸福的世界
