Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.90,0:20:15.67,VIOLET-song,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}Get over, no worries
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.80,0:20:20.84,VIOLET-song,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}Cause nothing is more precious than love
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.08,0:20:23.51,VIOLET-song,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}Noble… Faithful…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.55,0:20:27.41,VIOLET-song,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}She's as pure as the driven snow
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.71,0:20:32.85,VIOLET-song,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}Oh, dear heart… So sweat
