Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.96,0:20:46.07,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}许多人的思念 从天而降
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.15,0:20:50.08,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}薇尔莉特
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.17,0:20:59.01,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.93,0:21:04.49,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}致亲爱的基尔伯特少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.75,0:21:12.41,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}您还好吗 别来无恙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.42,0:21:15.85,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}您现在在哪儿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.17,0:21:19.38,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是否有什么困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.19,0:21:28.72,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不论春夏秋冬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.80,0:21:31.73,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}四季轮转
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.50,0:21:36.54,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}惟独有少佐的季节迟迟不来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.49,0:21:41.53,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我原本并不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.83,0:21:46.50,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我一点也不懂少佐的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.80,0:21:52.86,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}可是在少佐所给予我的崭新人生中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.44,0:21:58.40,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我稍微能感受到一些了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.52,0:22:01.76,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}通过代写书信
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.07,0:22:04.90,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}通过遇到的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.39,0:22:12.37,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我相信着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.51,0:22:17.73,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}少佐还在某处活着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.37,0:22:20.66,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}所以我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.79,0:22:24.95,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}一直 一直活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.12,0:22:29.35,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}即使不知道前途会有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.01,0:22:31.11,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}也要一直活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.39,0:22:36.81,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}如果还能再次相见
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.53,0:22:39.00,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我想告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.57,0:22:42.57,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我现在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.38,0:22:44.51,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}稍微明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.23,0:22:55.76,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}「爱」的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.01,0:24:18.51,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}薇尔莉特 有代笔委托 非常紧急
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.59,0:24:21.60,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}贝内迪克特 你去泡茶
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.06,0:24:24.46,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}为什么啊 为什么我要去泡茶
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.11,0:24:32.04,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}薇尔莉特 客人在等你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.78,0:24:39.46,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我现在过去
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.48,0:26:29.02,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.95,0:26:33.29,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}只要客人有要求 不论身在何处 都能为您服务
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.22,0:26:35.95,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我是自动手记人偶服务
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.94,0:26:42.99,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}薇尔莉特·伊芙加登
